HEADWORD: Corbel-table
<hw>Cor"bel-ta`ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>A horizontal row of corbels, with the panels or filling between
them; also, less properly used to include the stringcourse on
them.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

